content: Subzone of Jurong East Planning Area in Singapore **Sungei Jurong** (also known as the **Jurong River**) is a river in [Jurong East](/wiki/Jurong_East), Singapore. The Jurong River subzone runs across this river. The subzone is bounded by the [Ayer Rajah Expressway](/wiki/Ayer_Rajah_Expressway), Jurong Port Road, Jalan Buroh and Penjuru Road.
